{"tid":2461611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我一直都仲好鍾意我小學同學，個腦全部都係佢既樣","createTime":"2021-03-25T13:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:26:50.000Z","uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2e9bdddaaeef21855ee036afaf9184e2f78154","tid":2461611,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"其實呢十幾年我心裡面都仲有你<br />\n成日都會喺夢裡面見到你<br />\n近排我地因為某d事我地再見返面<br />\n傾返好多以前既事<br />\n令到我所有回憶、感覺都湧晒出黎<br />\n記返起我以前會喺窗口望住等你經過<br />\n我望住你仍然會心跳加速<br />\n我仍然好鍾意你對大眼晴<br />\n我仍然好鍾意你對住我傻笑<br />\n<br />\n雖然你知道我鍾意左你好耐<br />\n但係我真係好想親口同你講<br />\n「我好鍾意你」<br />\n每當我想講之際我都吞返句說話落肚<br />\n因為你都已經有一齊左好耐既女朋友<br />\n<br />\n呢十幾年黎我間唔中會因為d小事搵下你<br />\n我只係唔想同你斷左聯絡<br />\n唔想你喺我生命中消失<br />\n就算只係同你keep住呢種關係已經足夠了<br />\n我對你既感覺會一直放喺心入面一個重要既位置<br />\n唔打擾係最後既温柔"},{"pid":"a566333a6948836271011797756c1f4941b5a7ca","tid":2461611,"uid":355064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔打擾係最後既温柔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f1141f43f5ad9bc976129431ef80a935be7916","tid":2461611,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81c2b34c66892c3cdd340a672c1b3d2216cba4f","tid":2461611,"uid":183520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"你鍾意既只係一段回憶同幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99be53f6b19f059e1c3c56bb43b9775b4d3ffe51","tid":2461611,"uid":229353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:08:28.000Z","msg":"你今日都幾得閒=="},{"pid":"17868cb023dc88c2421f5de5fbad9a63a4e85547","tid":2461611,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s